text: McKinley is an unincorporated community, in Abington Township, Montgomery County, Pennsylvania, United States. McKinley is located along Forrest Avenue between Pennsylvania Route 73 (Township Line Road) and Jenkintown Road southeast of Jenkintown. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Montgomery County, Pennsylvania Category:Unincorporated communities in Pennsylvania
